Why Grafana + InfluxDB?

Real-time data monitoring for timely visibility into test activities and trends.

Optimized for time-series data, making it ideal for tracking metrics over time.

Flexible, customizable dashboards tailored to QA and engineering needs.

Easy integrations with automation frameworks, CI/CD pipelines, and test tools.

Lightweight and performant, even with large volumes of test results.

Open-source and cost-effective, enabling rapid implementation without heavy overhead.

Powerful alerting capabilities to flag quality issues proactively.



